&lt;p&gt;&lt;span helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot;&gt;目睹了全球变暖对南极洲造成的影响，又想到这些极地动物们将要面临的未来，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot;&gt;摄影师在拍摄的最后一天&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot;&gt;忍不住掉下眼泪&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot;&gt;：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

